James Hansen (91) Defensive Line  - NEVADA CAREER
RS SENIOR (2023): Started all 12 games ... Had 4.5 tackles-for-loss and a sack among his 18 tackles on the year
data.text:
NEVADA CAREER

RS SENIOR (2023): Started all 12 games ... Had 4.5 tackles-for-loss and a sack among his 18 tackles on the year ... Made a tackle-for-loss among his two solo tackles against Idaho (Sept. 9) ... Had a tackle-for-loss against Kansas (Sept. 16) ... Made two tackles (one solo) at both Fresno State (Sept. 30) and against UNLV (Oct. 14) ... Had three tackles (one solo) at San Diego State (Oct. 21) ... Recorded two tackles-for-loss, including a sack, against Hawai'i (Nov. 4) ... Shared a tackle-for-loss, broke up a pass, and made three tackles at Utah State (Nov. 11).

RS JUNIOR (2022): Appeared in 12 games, making six starts ... Started the final six games of the season ... Finished with 19 tackles, including a sack, 3.0 tackles-for-loss, and a forced fumble ... Had a strip-sack that was recovered by Nevada, against Texas State (Sept. 3) ... Made three tackles (two solo) at Air Force (Sept. 23) ... Had a tackle-for-loss among his five tackles (two solo) against San Diego State (Oct. 22) ... Shared tackles-for-loss at San José State (Oct. 29) and against Fresno State (Nov. 19).

UTAH STATE CAREER

JUNIOR (2021): Redshirt season ... Did not appear in any games.

SOPHOMORE (2020): Played in five games and made his first-career start against Fresno State (11/14)… Finished the season with nine tackles (1-solo, 8-assist) and one quarterback hurry… Had a season-high three stops against both New Mexico (11/26) and Air Force (12/3)… Added two stops against FS.

RIVERSIDE CC CAREER

FRESHMAN (2019): Earned first-team all-Southern California Football Association (SCFA) Southern Regional honors as a defensive lineman during his freshman season at Riverside (California) Community College... Helped the Tigers to a perfect 12-0 record and an appearance in the 2019 California Community College Athletic Association (CCCAA) State Championship game... Recorded 23.0 tackles, which included 2.0 sacks and 4.0 tackles for loss, while adding one forced fumble on the year... Had a season-high nine tackles against El Camino JC.
